			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>I was taking a gander through Reed's spreadsheet yesterday and there is a seperate number column for amplification.
<br />

<br />
Can you bard gurus provide an example of where amplification is most useful?  I know it lasts for 5 ticks but I am unsure of where to fit it in and for what benefit.  Do you guys have any combo sets or other advice about using this?
<br />

<br />
</span></td>
