				<td><img src="/skins/default/images/user_IsOffline.gif" alt="Scambon is not online. Last active: 2/19/2004 11:52:15 AM" border="0" />&nbsp;<a class="SmallBoldText" href="/User/UserProfile.aspx?UserName=Scambon">Scambon</a><br></td>
